text: I'm a Celebrity...Get Me Out of Here! returned for its twenty-second series on 6 November 2022 on ITV.The series returned to Murwillumbah, New South Wales, Australia, for the first time since 2019, following the easing of travel restrictions surrounding the COVID-19 pandemic. Ant & Dec returned to present the series. Category:I'm a Celebrity...Get Me Out of Here! Category:2020s television seasons Category:2022 in entertainment
